Label: All countries of last or next residence
European Union
Description: European Union estimates are for the EU15 up to 2003, the EU25 from 2004 - 2006, the EU27 from 2007 and the EU28 from July 2013. Estimates are also shown separately for the EU15, the EU8 and the EU2.

Label: European Union EU27
Description: The EU25 plus Bulgaria and Romania

Label: European Union EU25
Description: The EU15 and the EU8 groupings plus Malta and Cyprus

Label: European Union EU15
Description: Austria, Belgium, Denmark, Finland, France, Germany, Greece, Republic of Ireland, Italy, Luxembourg, Netherlands, Portugal, Spain and Sweden

Label: European Union EU8
Description: Czech Republic, Estonia, Hungary, Latvia, Lithuania, Poland, Slovakia and Slovenia

Label: European Economic Area (EEA)
Description: Includes European Union countries plus Iceland, Liechtenstein and Norway

Label: European Free Trade Association (EFTA)
Description: Includes European Union countries plus Iceland, Liechtenstein, Norway and Switzerland.

Label: Non-EU
Description: Excludes migrants to and from European Union countries

Label: Commonwealth All
Description: From 2004 onwards, excludes Malta and Cyprus.

Label: New Commonwealth
Description: From 2004 onwards, excludes Malta and Cyprus.
